<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xml:lang="en"><generator uri="https://jekyllrb.com/" version="4.4.1">Jekyll</generator><link href="https://alshedivat.github.io/fundamentals-of-music/feed.xml" rel="self" type="application/atom+xml"/><link href="https://alshedivat.github.io/fundamentals-of-music/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" hreflang="en"/><updated>2025-07-09T16:53:12+00:00</updated><id>https://alshedivat.github.io/fundamentals-of-music/feed.xml</id><title type="html">Fundamentals of Music</title><subtitle>A simple, whitespace theme for academics. Based on [*folio](https://github.com/bogoli/-folio) design. </subtitle><entry><title type="html">summary of work last week</title><link href="https://alshedivat.github.io/fundamentals-of-music/blog/2025/summary-of-work-past-week/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="summary of work last week"/><published>2025-07-07T09:55:30+00:00</published><updated>2025-07-07T09:55:30+00:00</updated><id>https://alshedivat.github.io/fundamentals-of-music/blog/2025/summary-of-work-past-week</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://alshedivat.github.io/fundamentals-of-music/blog/2025/summary-of-work-past-week/"><![CDATA[<p>I managed to upload all of the files, as well as make a table of contents for the byauthor and bygenus pages.</p>]]></content><author><name></name></author><category term="pre-publishing"/><category term="building"/><category term="early"/><summary type="html"><![CDATA[summary]]></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">by authors page fixing</title><link href="https://alshedivat.github.io/fundamentals-of-music/blog/2025/the-tables-live/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="by authors page fixing"/><published>2025-07-02T19:56:30+00:00</published><updated>2025-07-02T19:56:30+00:00</updated><id>https://alshedivat.github.io/fundamentals-of-music/blog/2025/the-tables-live</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://alshedivat.github.io/fundamentals-of-music/blog/2025/the-tables-live/"><![CDATA[<p>I have succesfully formatted the “by authors” page. All the audio files are working. The tables are working. Huzzah.</p>]]></content><author><name></name></author><category term="pre-publishing"/><category term="building"/><category term="early"/><summary type="html"><![CDATA[the tables live!]]></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">audio formatting success!</title><link href="https://alshedivat.github.io/fundamentals-of-music/blog/2025/audio-formatting-success/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="audio formatting success!"/><published>2025-06-30T11:58:35+00:00</published><updated>2025-06-30T11:58:35+00:00</updated><id>https://alshedivat.github.io/fundamentals-of-music/blog/2025/audio-formatting-success</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://alshedivat.github.io/fundamentals-of-music/blog/2025/audio-formatting-success/"><![CDATA[<p>All of the audio files are working in the various locations! Moreover, they’re not beyond the confines of their cards, so they’re not justting out of the blocks.</p>]]></content><author><name></name></author><category term="pre-publishing"/><category term="building"/><category term="early"/><summary type="html"><![CDATA[home stretch]]></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">figuring out audio.liquid</title><link href="https://alshedivat.github.io/fundamentals-of-music/blog/2025/figuring-out-audio-liquid/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="figuring out audio.liquid"/><published>2025-06-26T11:28:15+00:00</published><updated>2025-06-26T11:28:15+00:00</updated><id>https://alshedivat.github.io/fundamentals-of-music/blog/2025/figuring-out-audio-liquid</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://alshedivat.github.io/fundamentals-of-music/blog/2025/figuring-out-audio-liquid/"><![CDATA[<p>After much agonizing, I was able to figure out how to add project audio to the project page. This will, of course, allow me to make all of the audio files playable from a single page without having to rebuild the project formatting by scratch. So that’s a win!</p>]]></content><author><name></name></author><category term="pre-publishing"/><category term="building"/><category term="early"/><summary type="html"><![CDATA[wading through the liquid]]></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">Short work</title><link href="https://alshedivat.github.io/fundamentals-of-music/blog/2025/short-work/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Short work"/><published>2025-06-25T11:58:30+00:00</published><updated>2025-06-25T11:58:30+00:00</updated><id>https://alshedivat.github.io/fundamentals-of-music/blog/2025/short-work</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://alshedivat.github.io/fundamentals-of-music/blog/2025/short-work/"><![CDATA[<p>I was able to change the color of a lot of things on the website from purple to blue; this only applies in light mode. I’m currently trying to figure out how to add audio files to project pics, but the process is confusing and liquid is fighting me the whole way.</p>]]></content><author><name></name></author><category term="pre-publishing"/><category term="building"/><category term="early"/><summary type="html"><![CDATA[recap of work done in an hour after session]]></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">Cleaning Up</title><link href="https://alshedivat.github.io/fundamentals-of-music/blog/2025/cleaning-up/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Cleaning Up"/><published>2025-06-22T23:10:53+00:00</published><updated>2025-06-22T23:10:53+00:00</updated><id>https://alshedivat.github.io/fundamentals-of-music/blog/2025/cleaning-up</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://alshedivat.github.io/fundamentals-of-music/blog/2025/cleaning-up/"><![CDATA[<p>Most of the extraneous pages have been removed, as have lots of the things on the front page. I’m going to build up the collection of files on the website soon; I do need to figure out how I want to format the “by author” and “by genus” pages; there will probably be a decent deal of css.</p>]]></content><author><name></name></author><category term="pre-publishing"/><category term="building"/><category term="early"/><summary type="html"><![CDATA[summary of some weekend work]]></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">Learning the site</title><link href="https://alshedivat.github.io/fundamentals-of-music/blog/2025/learning-the-site/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Learning the site"/><published>2025-06-20T11:58:39+00:00</published><updated>2025-06-20T11:58:39+00:00</updated><id>https://alshedivat.github.io/fundamentals-of-music/blog/2025/learning-the-site</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://alshedivat.github.io/fundamentals-of-music/blog/2025/learning-the-site/"><![CDATA[<p>Today I fixed the unicode symbols for the search bar and the light/dark mode toggle. I’ve also worked out what layouts would be most effective for presenting the informaiton.</p>]]></content><author><name></name></author><category term="pre-publishing"/><category term="building"/><category term="early"/><summary type="html"><![CDATA[coworking time update]]></summary></entry></feed>